2026-05-16T01:49:40.3717931Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3718742Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3719913Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3721284Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3722192Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3722882Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3723381Z 20    -->
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3724039Z 21    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
