2026-05-16T01:49:40.3726000Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:22-78
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3726718Z 22    <!--
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3727236Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3727891Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3728504Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3729294Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3730049Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3761802Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3762702Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3763490Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3764234Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3764939Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3765477Z 33    -->
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3766048Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3767009Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
2026-05-16T01:49:40.3768298Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:22-76
