2026-05-16T01:49:40.4374829Z 226            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T01:49:40.4375869Z 227            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T01:49:40.4376536Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T01:49:40.4377236Z 229            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T01:49:40.4378051Z 230            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T01:49:40.4378815Z 231            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T01:49:40.4379597Z 232            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-16T01:49:40.4380249Z 233            preserve via tools:node="merge".
